HEADWORD: exhibitionist
<hw>exhibitionist</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a person with a
compulsive desire to expose the genitals; -- usually a male.</def>
<wns>[wns=1]</wns>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> flasher.</syn>
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>someone who deliberately behaves in such a way as to
attract attention.</def> <wns>[wns=2]</wns>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> show-off.</syn>
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>exhibitionistic</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>exhibitionist</ent>⟦br⟧
